                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group" style="display: block;">

                            <p id="dvsiteTable" class="hidden" style="text-align:center;"> <b>Note :</b> There is no site available for the selected ring. You can rearrange the rings below for the topology plan.</p>
